data.description: Wait no more! You have found the home of your dreams! Welcome to one of the most sought after properties situated within the tranquil community of Vista Monte in Laguna Niguel. Placed in a prime location at the end of a single loaded street, this house is tucked away at the neighborhood's end, inviting guests to be amazed by a beautiful waterfall in the front entrance and backyard.Upon entering, you are immediately greeted by an expansive open floor plan that effortlessly blends comfort and charm. The meticulous layout seamlessly integrates the living, dining, and kitchen areas, ideal for both intimate family gatherings and entertaining guests. Upgraded kitchen appliances and recessed lighting imbue the home with a sense of warmth. Every detail down to custom stained glass windows, solar panels, and a central vacuum system has been thoughtfully considered. This includes generous parking with a three car garage, four car driveway and additional RV capability. Not to mention, the entire home has been repiped with PEX plumbing to give buyers a peace of mind. This home boasts 3 spacious bedrooms upstairs, including one room downstairs that is being used as an office but can be easily converted to a bedroom leading to a convenient bathroom around the corner. You will also find an upstairs bonus room for multiple utilities. The master bedroom is characterized by high ceilings that effortlessly flow into the master bathroom, echoing spaciousness and comfort. Moving to the backyard, you will be relaxed by the trickling sounds of the waterfall. The backyard offers a peaceful retreat. Additionally, due to the community amenities, this home in Vista Monte offers more than just a place to live; it provides a place to thrive. The low HOA dues here give you access to a picnic for those lazy Sunday afternoons , basketball court and tennis courts for friendly matches. Fire up the grill at the BBQ area or take a scenic ride on the nearby biking trails; it's all here waiting for you to call this special place home.
